exts' : ∀ {Δ Γ Γ'} → Subst Δ Γ Γ' → Subst (Δ ,·) (ctxWeaken Γ) (ctxWeaken Γ')
exts' {Γ = Γ , _} σ Z = ⊢-typeRename S_ (σ Z)
exts' {Γ = Γ , _} σ (S x) = exts' (σ ∘ S_) x

