ext'-typeWeaken : ∀ {Δ Γ Γ'} → (ρ : Rename Δ Γ Γ') → ∀ {A} → ext' ρ ∘ ∋-map typeWeaken ≗  ∋-map typeWeaken ∘ ρ {A}
